				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="527" y="12" width="240" arrowStyle="top: 85px;" />
				<text style="margin-bottom:10px;"><![CDATA[Jian did the right thing by not approving the facilitation payment and by coming to us to report his concerns about the supplier's request. We’ll take it from here.]]></text>
				<text ><![CDATA[We also assured Jian there is some flexibility in the penalty clause of the customer contract – delays that are outside of our control do not trigger the penalties.]]></text>
